{"title":"我扛起了枪","authors":["郑书村"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扛起了枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔朝鲜〕郑书村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扛起了枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给我的枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这支枪中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包含着无限沉重的分量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对着枪，我反复地思想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风雪呼啸的密林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时战士们若不拿起枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我就无法生活在祖国的大地上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了一支枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们流下了多少鲜血！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志们，接过枪！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这声音此刻激荡着我的胸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，我接过了那支枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给了我那支枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是师团，不是军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是全民把它扛在钢铁般的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩膀上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不分前线和后方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强大呵，战无不胜的武装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山巍巍，江河滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的江山是铁壁铜墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扛起了枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪呵，你是党给的最神圣的武装！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和你永远守在机器旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一起站在酣睡的婴儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫丰收的稻浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫亲吻大地的春阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫红色的街道和青春火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热的耳语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到那远山中湍流的一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫她，保卫她！枪呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了她，先辈们行军二十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们嘴唇焦裂，手脚冻僵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫他们鲜血换来的珍贵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的一切……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着寒风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏破密林的长夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前辈把枪交给我们一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扛起了枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔全有译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}